Package: GetEdgarData
Type: Package
Title: Imports Financial Statements from the Edgar system (SEC/US)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Marcelo S. Perlin
Maintainer: Marcelo S. Perlin <marceloperlin@gmail.com>
Description: Downloads and parses zip files form the DERA systam at EDGAR (<https://www.sec.gov/dera/data>)Imports time series data from the Quandl database <https://www.quandl.com>. 
   Uses local caching for speeding up queries. 
